replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:02:33.000Z","msg":"田北辰搶嘴到 下次選立法會冇人同你配票"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:18:39.000Z","msg":"馬屎坑個位俾佢做嘅話, 佢先唔做議員"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T05:01:33.000Z","msg":"田北辰於2001 - 2007年任九廣鐵路公司管理局主席<br />\n馬時亨於2002－2007年財經事務及庫務局局長，財經局局長必然兼任九廣鐵路公司管理局成員<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擺明兩條友有牙齒印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7fce767b7d269e4cebdc6f9fd1c3b60ce2a2e11","tid":716101,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"1萬中既20條 變20%<br />\n<br />\n你今次重唔仆街"},{"pid":"d6cf501297b4416e1324ac98eee6a8342baa2cf7","tid":716101,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ba856e3957b1f92983727f7bf7eb32591b6c5a0","tid":716101,"uid":179467,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T05:41:18.000Z","msg":"唔係中科? 佢放料出黎"},{"pid":"1c4f465109776e30a493a8b3572b9f7efbc85d51","tid":716101,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ba856e3957b1f92983727f7bf7eb32591b6c5a0","tid":716101,"uid":179467,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}